tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE website_traffic_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url VARCHAR(255),
    date_visited TIMESTAMP,
    referrer_url VARCHAR(255),
    user_agent VARCHAR(255),
    time_spent_on_page INT
);

CREATE TABLE website_traffic_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url TEXT,
    visit_date TIMESTAMP,
    visit_duration INT,
    visitor_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE marketing_performance_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_id INT,
    website_traffic_id INT,
    clicks INT,
    impressions INT
);

CREATE TABLE website_visits (
  visit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  visit_date DATE,
  page_url VARCHAR(255),
  visitor_ip VARCHAR(50),
  referrer_url VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE click_rates (
  click_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  visit_id INT,
  click_time TIMESTAMP,
  click_location VARCHAR(50),
  click_source VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE search_queries (
  query_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  query_text TEXT,
  search_time TIMESTAMP,
  search_location VARCHAR(50),
  search_results_count INT
)

CREATE TABLE website_performance (
  page_url VARCHAR(255) PRIMARY KEY,
  load_time_ms INT,
  status_code INT
)

CREATE TABLE referrer_sites (
  site_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  site_url VARCHAR(255),
  site_description TEXT,
  site_category VARCHAR(50)
)
